trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines whether a <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox"></xref> control contains files that have read-only attributes.

trans-unit.source: Use the `ReadOnly` property for a <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox> control to specify whether files that have read-only attributes are displayed in the file list or not.
trans-unit.target: Använd den `ReadOnly` -egenskapen för en <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>kontroll för att specificera om filer som har skrivskyddad visas i listan eller inte.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.Normal%2A> property is set to `true` (the default), files that have read-only attributes are displayed regardless of the `ReadOnly` property setting.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Om den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.Normal%2A>egenskapen `true` (standard), filer som har skrivskyddad visas oberoende av den `ReadOnly` egenskapsinställning.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.Normal%2A>

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om filer som har den <xref uid="langword_csharp_ReadOnly" name="ReadOnly" href=""> </xref> attributet kommer att visas, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
